videos.description: Shockers throw a bad pass and Quinton Rose intercepts to hammer it down for a dunk.
videos.headline: Owls'  Rose posterizes on dunk

videos.description: The ball gets kicked around the arc and finds Shaquille Morris who makes the long ball.
videos.headline: Shockers' Morris drains easy 3

videos.description: Darral Willis Jr. drives into the paint and lays one while drawing the foul, but would miss the free throw.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Willis drives in for a layup

videos.description: The ball gets kicked out to Conner Frankamp who drives into the paint for the jumper.
videos.headline: Shockers' Frankamp with the smooth jumper

videos.description: Quinton Rose drives in for the layup and the ball gets swatted away by Shaquille Morris.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Morris rejects Rose at the rim

videos.description: Both teams scramble on the floor to get possession of the ball, ending with Wichita State's Conner Frankamp lays it in.
videos.headline: Scuffle on floor leads to a Shocker lay-in

videos.description: Zach Brown misses the triple, but Shaquille Morris is there to clean up for the lay-in and the foul.
videos.headline: Morris' and-1 bucket gives the Shockers the lead
